 +-------+-----+------+------+-------+------+---+---------------+---------+
 |nobreak|pub  | 0/33 |  3.0M| 980901| 12/97| 10|[V][C][S][s][L]|[D][s][L]|
 +-------------+------+------+-------+------+---+---------------+---------|
 |  qna  |pub  | 0/13 |  0.0M| 980831| 1/301| 23|[V][C][S][s][L]|[D][s][L]|
 +-------------+------+------+-------+------+---+---------------+---------|
 |  test |empty| 0/67 |  0.0M| 980911| 4/201| 14|[V][C][S][s][L]|[D][s][L]|
 +-------------+------+------+-------+------+---+---------------+---------|
